msgid ""
"KeePassRX is password manager for KeePass databases, designed for Ubuntu "
"Touch. It is licensed under the GNU AGPL v3 license."
msgstr ""
"KeePassRX è un gestore password per i database KeePass, progettato per "
"Ubuntu Touch. È rilasciato sotto licenza GNU AGPL v3."

msgid ""
"The built-in KeePass icon images are licensed under a variety of licenses as "
"detailed in assets/COPYING."
msgstr ""
"Le icone integrate in KeePass sono rilasciate sotto varie licenze come "
"specificato in assets/COPYING."

